  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4532444">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4532444/" class="title-link">喜欢这本书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4532444"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/xxf1988/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u48099007-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/xxf1988/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">小猫</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-12-17"
      class="main-meta">2010-12-17 16:38:26</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4532444_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  书看完了，回过头来，仔细想想，感觉中国历史在自己脑海里清晰了好多。通史是以粗线条的形式为中国历史描一轮廓，让读者对历史知识形成框架，和整体的感观。比如春秋五霸兴起如何更替；战国七雄如何一一并入强秦；汉武如何奋起，轮台诏如何挽西汉于崩溃边缘；王莽的改革与败亡...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4532444/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">10有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_4532444_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_4532444_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5032290">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5032290/" class="title-link">整合的魅力</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5032290"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/36771726/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u36771726-14.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/36771726/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">唐山</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-07-21"
      class="main-meta">2011-07-21 15:32:43</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5032290_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  傅乐成先生是台湾著名历史学家，傅斯年大师的侄子，本书写于1960年，以后不断修正，直至1978年。  今天的学者，大体不敢写通史，因为需要的阅读量太大，犯错误的可能太多，而超越前人的可能又太小。写通史，莫若说是一种炫耀，学力并不最重要，在学术圈中的身份与地位更关键。 ...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5032290/#comments">(6回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">22有用 / 3没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
